<TEXT>
please doesnt anybody out there love a 
bureaucrat 
last june entrepreneur matthew lesko launched my favorite 
bureaucrat contest and invited people around the country to 
submit a brief verifiable story of 250 words or less about how a 
government bureaucrat helped you 
lesko offered a 5000 cash prize for the winning entry and 
