which will fall into earths atmosphere in february unless it is 
plucked from its decaying orbit 
the satellite contains experiments related to the proposed 
star wars system to defend the united states against incoming 
warheads the experiments were meant to determine how materials 
that might be used in a star wars system will fare in the hostile 
environment of space 
