college curriculum which would cover five areas of knowledge 
but a good part of the pressure is being put on the wrong 
institutions students arrive in college having had 12 or more 
years of formal schooling what the test results show is that they 
are being cheated in their elementary and high schools not that 
the colleges have failed 
