expect that the lower mortgage rates this fall will keep boosting 
sales in the moderateprice range tuccillo said 
the most expensive housing market in september was the 
northeast where a medianpriced home went for 144800 followed 
by the west at 144300 the median sales price in the south was 
84200 while the midwest offered the cheapest housing with a 
median price of 71800 in september 
the national sales pace of 363 million units was the fastest 
clip since homes were sold at a seasonally adjusted annual rate of 
392 million units last december 
