hinsons conservative car and attention to detail reflect the 
attitude that has made this scrappy regional carrier survive the 
past decade to become what the 56yearold chairman and former 
fighter pilot calls an airline airline 
midway the last us airline certified in the era of regulation 
and first new one to fly under deregulation marks its 10th 
anniversary wednesday 
although it has less than 1 percent of the national airtravel 
